'''Black Panther''' (Japanese title name: ブラックパンサー ) is a [[beat 'em up]] [[arcade video game]] released by [[Konami]] in 1987.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Black Panther - Videogame by Konami |url=https://www.arcade-museum.com/game_detail.php?game_id=7137 |access-date=2023-05-15 |website=www.arcade-museum.com}}</ref> The player controls a cybernetic [[black panther]] cat who has to save the Earth by clawing, jumping, and shooting at enemies, collecting [[power-up]]s, and defeating [[boss (video gaming)|bosses]] to advance levels.

